overview: Johan and Ozlynn are a celebrity couple who have just been married a year. They have strange house rules that they cannot fight in the house even when they often 'fight' outside the home. At the height of their ego, the biggest issue they have to fight for is to celebrate Raya in who's village first. Unbeknownst to them, a huge surprise awaited them in the village for Raya this year.
title: Perang Jozlynn Balik Raya
